name: Meta-Heartbeat
description:
Welcome to meta-heartbeat, my first NFT drum video.

I believe that music and art can heal our souls. I was inspired by all the creative minds in the NFT community to create this song, as a common language, without barriers.
The video has a layer of a fractal that I made and animated to match the song, and it was inspired by a photograph from an NFT artist that I admire. It represents all the creativity that surrounds us.

This is my heartbeat.
